  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI DATE: July 31, 1950",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Chicago AIR MAIL",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "SUBJECT: [REDACTED], INFORMANT SPECIAL DELIVERY",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "O FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "On July 28, 1950, Mr. [REDACTED], phone [REDACTED], brought to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "this office the original letter and envelope attached, postmarked",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "July 25, 1950 at Chicago, which letter is quoted below:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "\"New Flying Saucer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "\"Since we are on the brink of a third world conflict, the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "world is more air concious than ever. Aviation in some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "phases is yet in its pioneering days. Much talk goes on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "about the flying saucers or discs. The saucer we speak",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "about, is not a military secret, and is not yet owned by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "any government. The flying saucer which was seen over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "South Chicago last April is a large fuel tank with crystal",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "glass wings. It has two large jet engines on both sides.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "It is radio controlled. It resembles a saucer very much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "when in flight. The wings cannot be seen on a clear day.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "This is so it is a most difficult target for anti aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "gunners. The reason for the large flat gas or fuel tank",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "is to give the ship a long range for atomic bombing. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "ship was designed by [REDACTED], a former 'Linco'",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "skywriter, [REDACTED], aircraft mechanic, and [REDACTED],",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "German World War I ace. The ship was financed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "by HOWARD HUGHES, millionaire aviation enthusiast. It is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "now being tested by the Glen F. Martin Aircraft Co., makers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of the Martin Marauder. The craft is only made for one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "way trips. It has a range of 4000 miles, ceiling of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "25,000 feet, and a speed of 750 miles per hour. So far",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "only a few of these craft have been made, and they usually",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "are pitched in the lake or ocean as they cannot be landed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "They are merely to carry a bomb of high destruction to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "'enemy country'. They have no wheels, but small steel rails",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "on the bottom from which they take off. All other mechanism",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "can be explained in detail. The man who welded the ship",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "says it is by far the best long range bombing instrument",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "he has ever seen. The name of the ship is the 'Danse",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Macabre'.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "\"Editor",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "\"In a few weeks zinc cuts showing 3 views of craft will be [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "sent to you.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
